    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase funding for schools so that pupils can catch up after COVID.",
        "additional_details": "Children have missed so much valuable classroom time. Schools need more trained staff to allow for smaller group work, to enable children to catch up properly. This funding needs to be available for the next two years.",
        "background": "The government need to extend the current funding model so that schools can decide at a local level how funds are best spent.",
